Overall. I would say this is on the minor list of faults that US President has made.  And even tho it was wrong. Its really not that big of a deal.   And its still not proven <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>(to those that live with their eyes closed)</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> that that Sadaam has / had WMD program.  The Isrealis knew what Sadaam was up to when they bombed his nuclear reactor.  They shut his ass down, or our troops would have had to face that nightmare in 1991.  If you really believe that Sadaam wasn't building that type of shit. Think about it.  He used / authorized the use of Chem / Bio weapons against Iran in the 80's.  He used them against his own people after the first Gulf war.  And theres probably a few other times, that there were no witness to tell the tale that he used them. His supply was cut off when the soviet union collapsed.  Since he couldnt buy them anymore from the russians. Why not just start a program of his own to build them. Its cheaper than buying them, and you dont get your supplies cut off.<br>
<br>
Get real.  You know deep down that fucker was just insane and was on a killing spree.  And it didnt sate` him just to kill 10 or 20 at a time.   100's, 1000's, 10,000's were his modus operandi.  There was one time during the Iran - Iraq war that he gassed his own troops, accidently. Oh well, no big loss there.  He repeated his pattern of murder on the grandest of scales over and over.  Yes, Sadaam was going for the Hilter / Stalin style of murder. <br>
<br>
Now , for those of you that are upset that we kicked the shit out of a murdering madman that was set on destruction on a mass scale.  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>And really feel that you need the proof</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  Think about it this way.  If a crazyman broke into your house, and held a gun to your wifes head, you, your child.  Would you wait for him to pull the trigger to put a cap in his ass? Do you need that type of proof?  Hell no you wouldnt.  You'd shoot his ass dead and hug your kids and be thankfull that you had the courage to do what was right, even tho it mean it cost someone else their life.  Thats what G.W. did.  And i'd support his ass again.  <br>
