How difficult would it be to hide a small nuke or a few tons of Sarin in a freighter and park it in NYC, LA, Galveston or any other coastal city harbor and turn 100,000+ americans into names on a plaque of rememberance.  I say no more.  If you know what they're gonna do, and its only a matter of time. Take em out.  I got your back.<br>
